<div class="card mb-3">
    <h2 class="card-title">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
        At FlavorShare, we take your privacy seriously. This policy describes how we collect, 
        use, and protect your personal information when you use our recipe sharing platform.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="card mb-3">
    <h2 class="card-title">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">We collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul style="margin-top: 1rem; margin-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Username, email address, and password when you register</li>
        <li><strong>Profile Information:</strong> Display name, bio, and profile picture (optional)</li>
        <li><strong>Recipe Content:</strong> Recipes, comments, and ratings you submit</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with the platform to improve our service</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="card mb-3">
    <h2 class="card-title">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">Your information is used to:</p>
    <ul style="margin-top: 1rem; margin-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        <li>Provide and maintain our recipe sharing service</li>
        <li>Allow you to create and share recipes with the community</li>
        <li>Enable social features like comments and likes</li>
        <li>Improve the platform based on usage patterns</li>
        <li>Send important service-related communications</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="card mb-3">
    <h2 class="card-title">Data Security</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. 
        Passwords are hashed and never stored in plain text. However, no method of 
        transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="card mb-3">
    <h2 class="card-title">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">You have the right to:</p>
    <ul style="margin-top: 1rem; margin-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
        <li>Access your personal information</li>
        <li>Update or correct your account details</li>
        <li>Delete your account and associated data</li>
        <li>Export your recipes</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="card mb-3">
    <h2 class="card-title">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
        We use essential cookies to maintain your session and preferences. These are 
        necessary for the proper functioning of the website.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h2 class="card-title">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mt-2">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through 
        our support channels. We're happy to address any concerns you may have.
    </p>
</div>

